com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se

Class NAPTR

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.NAPTR
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Appendable, java.io.Serializable

    public class NAPTR
extends java.lang.Object
implements Appendable
    This class models Naming Authority Pointer (NAPTR) resource records. Naming Authority Pointer (NAPTR) resource records are associated with ENUM domain names via the e164 extended create and update EPP commands. Instances of this class are used to construct NAPTR records to assign to ENUM domain objects, or to view attributes of NAPTR records already assigned to ENUM domain objects provisioned in an EPP Registry.
    See Also:
    Associate NAPTR records with a new ENUM domain object, rather than delegating to nameservers., Add or remove NAPTR record associations to/from an ENUM domain object., Report assocations between a domain object and NAPTRs., Serialized Form
